Happy 10th birthday to Damage Control 🥳

A decade of 'Damage Control' from @mat_zo. 

A genre-bending masterpiece, and the first in Mat’s career, it instantly solidified him as one of the most forward-thinking, fresh talents in dance music. The album spurned a @bbcradio1 Essential Mix in 2013 which is widely regarded by many as their favourite ever Essential Mix, and beyond that an expansive worldwide tour, including an album launch at @ministryofsoundclub in London. 

Over the last decade, Mat has retained his title as one of the most inventive artists on Anjunabeats, showcasing his ever-evolving style and continuing to capture the imagination of the masses.

To mark the occasion, we have repressed ‘Damage Control’ on a limited edition vinyl and included a previously-unheard album demo ‘LAXodus’, Mat’s Club Mix of ‘Pyramid Scheme’, as well as a selection of remixes from the likes of @andyc_ramagram, @croquetclubmusic and @pegboardnerds.

Available to pre-order now on the Anjuna Music Store, link in bio 🔗
